{"lemma":"سَلِيطٍ","slug":"سَلِيطٍ","root":"س.ل.ط","root_slug":"س-ل-ط","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ل-ط","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n20436"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%B7%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"fierce, bold, cheeky, sharp"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"sesame oil"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"vegetable oil"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"sesame"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Cognate with Aramaic שַׁלִּיטָ֣א (šallîṭā)\n\nProbably the same word as above."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n20436","headword_ar":"سَلِيطٌ","root":"slT","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Strong,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hard;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saliTN","text_ar":"سَلِطٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saloTN","text_ar":"سَلْطٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) You say, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAfirN saliTN","text_ar":"حَافِرٌ سَلِطٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saloTN","text_ar":"سَلْطٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saliyTN","text_ar":"سَلِيطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A strong,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hard, solid hoof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHaAfiri","text_ar":"الحَافِرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAb~apN saliTapu","text_ar":"دَابَّةٌ سَلِطَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A beast having a strong,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hard, hoof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxuf~i","text_ar":"الخُفِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baEiyrN saliTu","text_ar":"بَعِيرٌ سَلِطُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A camel having a strong,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hard, foot."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sharp;"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to anything. (K.) You say also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sanaAbiku saliTaAtN","text_ar":"سَنَابِكُ سَلِطَاتٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sharp edges of the fore parts of hoofs."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Chaste in speech,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eloquent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and sharp in tongue:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) an epithet of praise when applied to the male, and of dispraise when [with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":"] applied to the female: (IDrd, K:) also, (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"long-tongued;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saliTN","text_ar":"سَلِطٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saloTN","text_ar":"سَلْطٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saliyTapN","text_ar":"سَلِيطَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"salaTaAnapN","text_ar":"سَلَطَانَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siliTaAnapN","text_ar":"سِلِطَانَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siliT~aAnapN","text_ar":"سِلِطَّانَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M;) the last written [thus] with tesh-deed to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"T","text_ar":"ط"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the Jm., and there explained as signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"long-tongued and clamorous:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saliyTN","text_ar":"سَلِيطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clamorous and foul-tongued;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saliyTapN","text_ar":"سَلِيطَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a woman: (Msb:) or the latter, applied to a woman,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clamorous:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"long-tongued and vehemently clamorous:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saliyTapu All~isaAni","text_ar":"سَلِيطَةُ اللِّسَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is applied to a woman in two senses; signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sharp-tongued; and long-tongued."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, TA.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lisaAnN","text_ar":"لِسَانٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saliyTN","text_ar":"سَلِيطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saliTN","text_ar":"سَلِطٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saloTN","text_ar":"سَلْطٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A long tongue."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Oil of olives;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb, K;) so applied by the generality of the Arabs: but by the people of El-Yemen applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"oil of sesame,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sesamum:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M:) IDrd, in the Jm, says the reverse; and IF has followed him; but what J says is right, as Sgh, has observed in the O: (TA:) also, (K,) or as some say, (M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any oil expressed from grains"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"berries:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suloTaAnN","text_ar":"سُلْطَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb, K.)"}],"source_refs":["M","TA","S","K","IDrd","Msb","Lth"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}